title: “IT’S GOING TO HAPPEN!” | Bari Weiss Warns Us About AI
description:
I recently spoke with Bari Weiss, Founder and Editor of ‘The Free Press’ and host of the ‘Honestly’ podcast. I asked her about The Godfather of Google quitting over concerns about A.I and the spread of mis-information. Is AI the end of the world? Or the dawn of a new one? #ai #tech #technology 

Follow Bari’s Work Here: https://www.thefp.com/
